<div class="c10_1"> 
<div id="v10.1.1"><span class="H7225 s">In the beginning</span><span class="H430 s"> </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H1254 s"> </span></span><span class="H1254 s">created</span><span class="H853 s"> †</span><span class="H8064 s"> the heaven</span><span class="H853 s"> and</span><span class="H776 s"> the earth</span>.</div> 
<div id="v10.1.2"><span class="H776 s">And the earth</span><span class="H1961 s"> was</span><span class="H8414 s"> without form</span><span class="H922 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and void</span><span class="H2822 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">;</span></span></span> and darkness</span><span class="H6440 s"> <i>was</i> upon the face</span><span class="H8415 s"> of the deep</span><span class="H7307 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">.</span></span></span> And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H7307 s">the </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H7307 s"></span></span></span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H7307 s">Spirit</span><span class="H430 s"> of God</span><span class="H7363 s"> </span></span><span class="H7363 s">moved</span><span class="H5921 s"> upon</span><span class="H6440 s"> the face</span><span class="H4325 s"> of the waters</span>.</div> 
<div id="v10.1.3"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H559 s"> </span></span><span class="H559 s">said</span><span class="H1961 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> </span><span class="TheLordWords"><span class="H1961 s">Let there be</span><span class="H216 s"> light</span><span class="H216 s"><span class="punctuation"></span></span></span><span class="H216 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> and there was light</span>.</div> 
<div id="v10.1.4"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H7200 s"> </span></span><span class="H7200 s">saw</span><span class="H853 s"> †</span><span class="H216 s"> the light</span><span class="H3588 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> that</span><span class="H2896 s"> <i>it was</i> good</span><span class="H430 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> and </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H914 s"> </span></span><span class="H914 s">divided</span><span class="H996 s"> †</span><span class="H216 s"> the light</span><span class="H996 s"> from</span><span class="H2822 s"> the darkness</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> <span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">(</span></span></span>the light from…<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> Heb<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">.</span></span></span> between the light and between the darkness<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">)</span></span></span></span></div> 
