<div id="v10.1.6"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H559 s"> </span></span><span class="H559 s">said</span><span class="H7549 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> </span><span class="TheLordWords"><span class="H7549 s">Let there be a firmament</span><span class="H8432 s"> in the midst</span><span class="H4325 s"> of the waters</span><span class="H914 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and let it divide</span><span class="H4325 s"> the waters</span><span class="H4325 s"> from the waters</span><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">.</span></span> </span><span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> <span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">(</span></span></span>firmament<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> Heb<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">.</span></span></span> expansion<span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">)</span></span></span></span></div> 
<div id="v10.1.7"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H6213 s"> </span></span><span class="H6213 s">made</span><span class="H7549 s"> the firmament</span><span class="H914 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and divided</span><span class="H4325 s"> the waters</span><span class="H834 s"> which</span><span class="H8478 s"> <i>were</i> under</span><span class="H7549 s"> the firmament</span><span class="H4325 s"> from the waters</span><span class="H834 s"> which</span><span class="H5921 s"> <i>were</i> above</span><span class="H7549 s"> the firmament</span><span class="H3651 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> and it was so</span>.</div> 
<div id="v10.1.8"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H7121 s"> </span></span><span class="H7121 s">called</span><span class="H7549 s"> the firmament</span><span class="H8064 s"> </span><span class="TheLordWords"><span class="H8064 s">Heaven</span><span class="H6153 s"><span class="punctuation"></span></span></span><span class="H6153 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">.</span></span></span> And the evening</span><span class="H1242 s"> and the morning</span><span class="H8145 s"> were the second</span><span class="H3117 s"> day</span>.</div> 
<div id="v10.1.9"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H559 s"> </span></span><span class="H559 s">said</span><span class="H4325 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> </span><span class="TheLordWords"><span class="H4325 s">Let the waters</span><span class="H8064 s"> under the heaven</span><span class="H6960 s"> be gathered together</span><span class="H413 s"> unto</span><span class="H259 s"> one</span><span class="H4725 s"> place</span><span class="H3004 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and let the dry</span><span class="H7200 s"> <i>land</i> appear</span></span>: and it was so.</div> 
