<div id="v10.1.25"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H6213 s"> </span></span><span class="H6213 s">made</span><span class="H2416 s"> the beast</span><span class="H776 s"> of the earth</span><span class="H4327 s"> after his kind</span><span class="H929 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and cattle</span><span class="H4327 s"> after their kind</span><span class="H7431 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and every thing that creepeth</span><span class="H127 s"> upon the earth</span><span class="H4327 s"> after his kind</span><span class="H430 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> and </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H7200 s"> </span></span><span class="H7200 s">saw</span><span class="H2896 s"> that <i>it was</i> good</span>.</div> 
<div id="v10.1.26"><span class="H430 s">And </span><span class="TheLordTitles"><span class="H430 s">God</span><span class="H559 s"> </span></span><span class="H559 s">said</span><span class="H6213 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> </span><span class="TheLordWords"><span class="H6213 s">Let <span class="TheLordTitles">us </span>make</span><span class="H120 s"> man</span><span class="H6754 s"> in <span class="TheLordTitles">our </span>image</span><span class="H1823 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> after <span class="TheLordTitles">our </span>likeness</span><span class="H7287 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">:</span></span></span> and let them have dominion</span><span class="H1710 s"> over the fish</span><span class="H3220 s"> of the sea</span><span class="H5775 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and over the fowl</span><span class="H8064 s"> of the air</span><span class="H929 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and over the cattle</span><span class="H776 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and over all the earth</span><span class="H7431 s"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation"><span class="punctuation">,</span></span></span> and over every creeping thing</span><span class="H7430 s"> that creepeth</span><span class="H776 s"> upon the earth</span>.</span></div> 
